Getting to it? That's not the hard part.


... It's letting go.

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

This is a COLLABORATION between Gabriel Jade and myself, and our entry into Clichecon! Which cliches did we choose? Well all of them. If we have to boil it down to two, though:

A doorway (of any shape) to another dimension/timeline/world
(GOI/POI) gets one over the Foundation, making them look like fools in the process.


This was an absolute blast to write, and even more fun to brainstorm.

also we got HTML to work with listpages somehow, which was nice.
