Did Rhi-0 become the new SCP-4450? If so, why? I was under the impression the old SCP-4450 instances  to get their abilities and tied in with the debt.

When did Rhi-0 learn to edit the code? *How* did they edit the code? Does the casino have a computer to put in a new password with somewhere?

